---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us | Section 8 Calculator"
  description="Get in touch with the Section 8 Calculator team for questions, feedback, partnerships, or corrections."
>
  <article class="container prose" style="padding: 2.5rem 0 4rem; max-width: 42rem;">
    <h1>Contact Us</h1>

    <p>
      Have a question, found an error, or want to suggest an improvement? We'd love to hear
      from you. Section 8 Calculator is a small, independent project, and we read every message.
    </p>

    <h2>General Inquiries</h2>
    <p>
      For questions about the site, data corrections, or feedback:<br />
      <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@section8calculator.com">contact@section8calculator.com</a>
    </p>

    <h2>Common Questions</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>"Can you help me apply for Section 8?"</strong> — We are not a PHA and cannot process applications. Please contact your <a href="https://www.hud.gov/program_offices/public_indian_housing/pha/contacts">local Public Housing Authority</a> directly.</li>
      <li><strong>"Why doesn't my city show the right data?"</strong> — Our estimates are based on HUD's published income limits and Fair Market Rents. If you notice an error, please email us with your ZIP code and we'll investigate.</li>
      <li><strong>"Can I use your data or link to your site?"</strong> — Yes. We encourage housing counselors, nonprofits, and media to link to our resources.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Media & Partnerships</h2>
    <p>
      For press inquiries, partnership proposals, or collaboration requests:<br />
      <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@section8calculator.com">contact@section8calculator.com</a>
    </p>

    <h2>Response Time</h2>
    <p>
      We typically respond within <strong>1–3 business days</strong>. Please note that we
      cannot provide individual housing advice or eligibility determinations — for that, please
      contact your local PHA.
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <a href="/about/">About us</a> · <a href="/disclaimer/">Disclaimer</a>
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
